column3: KC-201: Add a UH specific Constants class as counterpart to community one. KC-306: Make performing organization required and prevent it from getting a default value during refresh. KC-515 Improve Project Summary validation KC-680 .... fix to improve budget finalization KC-764 If the modular budget checkbox is checked, the proposal cannot be "submitted to sponsor" for non S2S KC-815 Negotiation should populate with default data KC-892 Enforce some negotiation activity type entries to single occurrence per award
